{"data":[{"date":"08:41 02/08","title":"Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 18 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/18/olympic-iraq-rut-lui-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-18-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u1ee6y ban Olympic Iraq \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 18 sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i U16 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i.</h2><h2>Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean an ninh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n bay Baghdad (Iraq) \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n U16 Iraq do s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu gi\u1ea3 khi \u0111ang l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh sang Jordan h\u00f4m 30/7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean, IFA \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i U16. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ban \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 do \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n U16 Iraq \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, IFA \u0111\u00e3 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Ali Hadi v\u00e0 \u00ea-k\u00edp tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra, 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U16 Iraq b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u1edf s\u00e2n bay c\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/10/Olympic-Iraq-rut-lui-khoi-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Iraq quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft IFA s\u1ebd t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eebng m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tra nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c gian l\u1eadn c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn ra\u00a0tr\u00ean trang\u00a0Wikipedia\u00a0c\u1ee7a ASIAD 2018, tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Iraq \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb x\u00f3a t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea3ng C. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, trang\u00a0Soccer Iraq\u00a0c\u00f2n \u0111\u0103ng d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u201cIraq \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Asian Games 2018 do nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Olympic Iraq kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea3ng C m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u00a0Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Syria v\u00e0 Timor Leste. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7t ra nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng 3 \u0111\u1ed9i, hai b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u 5 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ba b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u 4 \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch th\u1ee9 ba t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4957","checkdouble":"192516"},{"date":"07:37 02/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 2/8: Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/6/1/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-28-sao-that-sung-cua-real-khuoc-tu-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 2/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u00e1n Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet.</strong> Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a The Kop \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb M.U. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chuy\u1ec3n sang Manchester United. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi gian qua. Nh\u01b0ng Kovacic kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi M.U v\u00ec c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 28 Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb M h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 28 Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb M h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-28-Sao-that-sung-cua-Real-khuoc-tu-M-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra tung t\u00edch c\u1ee7a sao M.U bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. </strong>Anthony Martial n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho r\u1eb1ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ea1i gia Italia ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha Matteo Darmian.</strong> Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a M.U. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1eabn \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o\u201d x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Milan ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.</strong> Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Rossoneri ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Gonzalo Higuain\" title=\"tien dao Gonzalo Higuain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Vuot-mat-AC-Milan,-Chelsea-muon-mua-Gonzalo-Higuain-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Higuain s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Sarri h\u1ee9a tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng sao tr\u1ebb 17 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Chelsea. </strong>Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi. T\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 17 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. </strong>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Shaka Hislop m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean Everton. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y n\u00ean tr\u00e1nh xa trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Man United n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng h\u1edb gi\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nPires d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</strong> Robert Pires d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Alexandre Lacazette. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tin \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng 20 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4956","checkdouble":"192511"},{"date":"08:41 02/08","title":"Barca nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/26/barca-nhan-don-dau-vu-rabiot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi PSG.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Rabiot</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho ra \u0111i, Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Rafinha v\u00e0 Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng. HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/PSG-chan-duong-Barca-mua-Adrien-Rabiot-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Barca r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Rabiot\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, song PSG v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. C\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng Rabiot mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi PSG do lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Tuchel.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh s\u1ee3 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb sau khi c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Julian Draxler \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG b\u00e1n Raniot, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho anh m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng. D\u00f9 PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-cho-them-7-ngay-de-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-psg-180-192423.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca v\u1eabn ch\u1edd th\u00eam 7 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Rabiot</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, sau \u0111\u00f3 Barca s\u1ebd v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean,\u00a0trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 Rabiot.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rabiot s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi PSG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"PSG ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Barca mua Adrien Rabiot h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/barca-nhan-don-dau-vu-rabiot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rabiot s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i l\u00e0 b\u1edfi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng m\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam\u00a04 n\u0103m k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi Rabiot nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 490.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y t\u1eeb PSG, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 ngay \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf l\u1ea1i thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4955","checkdouble":"192514"},{"date":"07:16 02/08","title":"HLV Sarri h\u1ee9a tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng sao tr\u1ebb 17 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-sarri-hua-trong-dung-sao-tre-17-tuoi-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi. T\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 17 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. </h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hudson-Odoi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, U17 Anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Callum Hudson-Odoi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 2000 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Antonio Conte trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Hudson-Odoi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Chelsea. \u0110\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Arsenal t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup, sao tr\u1ebb ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 18 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. D\u00f9 Chelsea th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 6-5 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m (h\u00f2a 1-1 sau 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh), Hudson-Odoi v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ng\u1ee3i khen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u1ee3i khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u1ee3i khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/tien-dao-Hudson-Odoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hudson-Odoi ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01a1i ch\u1ebfch v\u1ec1 b\u00ean tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Chelsea, Hudson-Odoi \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Hector Bellerin c\u1ee7a Arsenal kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh. Anh c\u00f2n ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty song Alvaro Morata \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri t\u1eb7ng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn, Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ef9 t\u1eeb. \u00d4ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho sao tr\u1ebb 17 tu\u1ed5i ra s\u00e2n trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. &ldquo;Hudson-Odoi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian&rdquo;, Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Hudson-Odoi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t, r\u1ea5t tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (\u0111\u1ed9i 1 Chelsea) trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri da khong the co duoc Golovin trong doi hinh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Chelsea-muon-mua-Lewandowski-cua-Bayern-Munich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Hudson-Odoi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u1ee3i khen</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlvaro Morata l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ecb anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1. \u0110ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin The Blues d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea9y ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 Morata c\u00f3 thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin hay kh\u00f4ng&rdquo;, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i th\u00eam. &ldquo;D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 Morata.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Arsenal 1-1 (pen 6-5) Chelsea:</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/2/Arsenal-vs-Chelsea_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-muon-da-tan-cong-phai-cho-kante-172-192492.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng? Ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd Kante</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mot-lat-cat-ve-maurizio-sarri-buoc-ra-anh-sang-phia-ben-kia-suon-doc-389-192482.html\">M\u1ed9t l\u00e1t c\u1eaft v\u1ec1 Maurizio Sarri: B\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nham-kovacic-trong-truong-hop-khong-co-duoc-ramsey-172-192463.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ee5 Aaron Ramsey</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/psg-chua-tu-bo-kante-172-192456.html\">PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf tham v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu sao s\u00e1ng Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barkley-quyet-tim-lai-vi-tri-o-chelsea-172-192452.html\">Barkley quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4954","checkdouble":"192509"},{"date":"08:22 02/08","title":"G\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea v\u1eabn b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u1ee5 \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/gui-loi-de-nghi-sieu-khung-chelsea-van-bi-tu-choi-vu-zaha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Danny Drinkwater song Crystal Palace \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Zaha</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard v\u00e0 Willian l\u00e0 2 trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. M.U \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Willian, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Chelsea-muon-mua-Wilfried-Zaha-voi-loi-de-nghi-cuc-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Zaha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hazard</span>, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Willian, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef Hazard v\u00e0 Willian, Chelsea c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Theo Mirror v\u00e0 ESPN, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Wilfried Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Zaha l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Palace. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh, Zaha s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Crystal Palace t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Zaha cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Wilfried Zaha, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Danny Drinkwater song Crystal Palace \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea v\u1eabn b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng, Chelsea v\u1eabn b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/1/Gui-loi-de-nghi-sieu-khung,-Chelsea-van-bi-tu-choi-vu-hang-thai-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Crystal Palace t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Zaha cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra \u0111i, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Zaha \u1edf l\u1ea1i. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a\u00a0Chelsea ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Palace ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t, thay v\u00ec nh\u1eadn 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 Drinkwater.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCrystal Palace mu\u1ed1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9ng kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Ngo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u sao M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Palace nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Man City c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Zaha, song l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mahrez.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4953","checkdouble":"192512"},{"date":"09:00 02/08","title":"Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/mourinho-muon-mu-chieu-mo-bo-doi-cua-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng M.U s\u1ebd chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kroos - Bale c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Marca, trong th\u1eddi gian qua, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 khao kh\u00e1t c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real l\u00e0 Toni Kroos v\u00e0 Gareth Bale. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean l\u00e0 hai trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Old Trafford \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh cho M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 M.U c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/16/HLV-Mourinho-muon-MU-chieu-mo-bo-doi-cua-Real--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0Toni Kroos l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real, Toni Kroos l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau mua s\u1eafm h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y t\u1eeb l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 Real l\u1eabn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao, l\u00ean t\u1edbi 107 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u01b0a ra cho Kroos l\u00e0 g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng khi\u1ebfn M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi cho Real kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Bale, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Real sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo. B\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Wales l\u00fac n\u00e0y hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u1ebft m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Los Blancos t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm vinh quang.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV\u00a0Mourinho \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n M.U s\u1ebd chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p khi Real kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Mourinho t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng vui trong th\u1eddi gian qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5 mua s\u1eafm, song ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u00f4ng trong c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4952","checkdouble":"192515"},{"date":"06:46 02/08","title":"\u201cTr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o\u201d x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Milan ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/8/trong-phao-xac-nhan-sap-den-milan-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Rossoneri ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Higuain \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi Milan</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, gi\u1eefa Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Gonzalo Higuain. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Milan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecf ra 18 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u01b0\u1ee3n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina m\u00f9a n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u Euro 1 n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf ph\u00eda c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Higuain. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2018 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 9,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a d\u00f9 Milan ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 7,5 tri\u1ec7u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do s\u00e1ng h\u00f4m qua khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi, HLV Gennaro Gattuso kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Higuain hay ch\u01b0a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/Ket-qua-C1---Thong-ke-tran-dau-Tottenham-1-2-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gonzalo Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc nh\u1ecf. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Higuain ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi AC Milan sau khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7t ng\u00e0y ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi 3 b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung, Higuain \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Sky Sport r\u1eb1ng: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ed5n, ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 5 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi\u201d, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Argentina n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c C\u0110V AC Milan v\u00e0 v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Juventus. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f4i su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Higuain t\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 55 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 105 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Anh c\u00f9ng Bianconeri \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n gi\u00e0nh 2 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 Coppa Italia c\u00f9ng 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2016/17 nh\u01b0ng thua Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chiellini-noi-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-192376.html\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/sep-lon-napoli-chi-trich-ronaldo-la-hop-dong-thuong-mai-176-192360.html\">S\u1ebfp l\u1edbn Napoli ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ronaldo l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/roi-juventus-buffon-mien-luon-binh-luan-ve-ronaldo-176-192279.html\">R\u1eddi Juventus, Buffon mi\u1ec5n lu\u00f4n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dan-dau-cuoc-dua-gianh-higuain-172-192257.html\">Chelsea chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-ban-3-cau-thu-mua-pogba-172-192247.html\">Juventus b\u00e1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4951","checkdouble":"192508"},{"date":"18:08 01/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Bahrain.</h2><h2>Olympic Pakistan thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Pakistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Pakistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Pakistan-team-in-Bahrain-for-practice-matches.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Pakistan \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Bahrain\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Pakistan\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i\u00a0Bahrain. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1eef t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Nam \u00c1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Trung \u0110\u00f4ng \u0111ang mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Olympic Pakistan. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB c\u1ee7a Bahrain. H\u1ecd thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Budaiya Club, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Riffa SC 1-0 v\u00e0\u00a0Sitra Club 2-0, c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Al-Ahli SC.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea1c quan v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV\u00a0Jos\u00e9 Antonio Nogueira sau khi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 52 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi\u00a0d\u1eabn d\u1eaft tuy\u1ec3n QG Pakistan c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD, Pakistan s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Nepal. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 b\u00ed \u1ea9n v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 l\u00e0 Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110TQG Pakistan ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u1ea1ng 201 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH FIFA khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n cho bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4950","checkdouble":"192493"},{"date":"22:16 01/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-hoc-lom-bai-tu-cua-nguoi-anh-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng tin kh\u00f4ng vui\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, thay v\u00ec s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u ba tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 15, 17, 21/8 nh\u01b0 l\u1ecbch c\u0169, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 \u2018li\u1ec1n t\u00f9 t\u00ec\u2019 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y 14, 16 v\u00e0 19/8. S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a qu\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat b\u1edbt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Pakistan ng\u00e0y 14/8, g\u1eb7p Nepal ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u2018th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng\u2019 g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/8. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thay v\u00ec 4 ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, tr\u00e1nh r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti (th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Cikarang, qu\u1eadn Bekasi, mi\u1ec1n t\u00e2y Java, Indonesia). Trong khi \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Patriot (c\u0169ng thu\u1ed9c Bekasi). C\u0169ng theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, hai tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e1 l\u00fac 16h00, c\u00f2n tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal \u0111\u00e1 l\u00fac 19h00.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c n\u1eefa \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n 8 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf hai b\u1ea3ng D, F thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu) tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00ean l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp, l\u00e0m quen s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm s\u00e2n ph\u1ee5 t\u1eadp c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 8 \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch c\u0169, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 11/8. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm h\u01a1n 1 ng\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh s\u1edbm 1 ng\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 g\u1eb7p Palestine, Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 t\u1edbi 7/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192487.html\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n cho bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4949","checkdouble":"192501"},{"date":"22:31 01/08","title":"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u2018r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n\u2019 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/trung-ve-bui-tien-dung-he-lo-ve-phuong-phap-ren-quan-loi-hai-cua-thay-park.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 1/8 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u2018r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n\u2019 m\u00e0 anh kh\u00e1 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eafc t\u1eeb HLV Park Hang Seo.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u 1/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb PVF. Nh\u00ecn chung t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/854_dmhl1694-15331285268411369056055.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng \u2018n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng\u2019 v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1nh ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p khi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u2018r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n\u2019 m\u00e0 anh kh\u00e1 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eafc t\u1eeb HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB Viettel n\u00f3i: \"Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp th\u1ea7y Park \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ea5y so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Th\u1ea7y y\u00eau c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm b\u1eaft l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt th\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ec1 ra. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kho\u1ea3ng hai ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp trung, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 xong gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea7n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, th\u1ea7y Park lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, t\u1ea1o ra c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, c\u00f2n khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n th\u00ec mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt t\u1ef1 tin\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh, trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Palestine tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 tin g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 Asiad. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 3 tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i c\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Palestine s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 3/8 t\u1edbi. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-tai-asiad-2018-gui-loi-canh-bao-toi-olympic-viet-nam-168-192493.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4948","checkdouble":"192502"},{"date":"23:25 01/08","title":"VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD: Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/30/vtv-bi-ep-gia-ban-quyen-asiad-tha-dau-mot-lan-roi-thoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t, vi\u1ec7c VTV th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ee3i khen.</h2><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM d\u00e0nh cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang gia t\u0103ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng &lsquo;h\u00e9t gi\u00e1&rsquo; \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e9p VTV ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n World Cup v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a h\u1ea1 nhi\u1ec7t th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin VTV kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AISAD 2018 v\u00ec chi ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 cao. Vi\u1ec7c b\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 4 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t quan t\u00e2m, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/ve-xem-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-re-bat-ngo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ASIAD, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft VTV c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i AFF Cup 2018, v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 4 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la. T\u1ef1u chung nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 do s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh BLV Quang Huy c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao cho \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu. Do \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0o c\u00f3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1, gi\u1ea3i \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t hot. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd tr\u1edf \u0111i, ta c\u1ee9 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nhanh l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u00e9p gi\u00e1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t Nam&rdquo;, BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y VTV \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn ph\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n th\u1ec3 thao v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p, d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>V\u1eabn c\u00f2n hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem ASIAD?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t cao t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ASIAD 2018 tung ra, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi 99% VTV s\u1ebd n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n k\u1ef3 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 18 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 VTV ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &quot;b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0ng&quot; v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t, nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.&nbsp;Ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1edb, VTV t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh v\u00ec chi ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 cao, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady t\u1edbi ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a hai t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Viettel v\u00e0 Vingroup, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 su\u00f4n s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VTV\" title=\"VTV\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/anh_wc2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>VTV kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecf ra h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu thi\u1ebfu nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTV c\u0169ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu b\u00ean b\u00e1n l\u00e0 KJSMWORLD CORP ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VTV chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a VTV l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o b\u00e1o ch\u00ed v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, VTV v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u1edd xem li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u00f3 h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hay kh\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VTV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1eebng l\u00ean hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ASIAD c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u00ean b\u00e1n ch\u1ecbu gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1, ho\u1eb7c VTV \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 'm\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e2n' \u0111\u1ee9ng sau t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3, chuy\u1ec7n mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eb1ng, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd &lsquo;ngh\u1ec9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rsquo; m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n th\u1ec3 thao - v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean&rsquo; nhanh ch\u00f3ng, sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup-168-192386.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-asiad-nguoi-ham-mo-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-khong-duoc-xem-aff-cup-168-192386.html\">Sau ASIAD, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem AFF Cup</span><br>\r\nSau khi VTV tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n AFF Cup v\u00ec m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/vtv-khong-mua-ban-quyen-asiad-2018-khong-the-xem-truc-tiep-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-192345.html\">VTV tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018: Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 do ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t cao khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4947","checkdouble":"192504"},{"date":"18:02 01/08","title":"Roma t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i coi Malcom kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/roma-tuc-toi-coi-malcom-khong-ton-tai-tren-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng nay, CLB AS Roma s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom v\u00e0 coi nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRoma v\u1eabn cay c\u00fa v\u00ec b\u1ecb l\u1eadt k\u00e8o<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 tai ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Malcom. Ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ecdi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp AS Roma, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, anh (v\u00e0 Bordeaux) quay ngo\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Barca, khi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Roma v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n bay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, Malcom \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Roma, khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng d\u1eady s\u00f3ng, cho r\u1eb1ng CLB Italia s\u1ebd&hellip; c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e9m g\u00e3y gi\u00f2 sao tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 cay c\u00fa xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter, khi Roma \u0111\u0103ng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, trong \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef c\u1ee7a Malcom c\u00f9ng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 26 b\u1ecb x\u00f3a b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, v\u00e0 Barca ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch x\u00f3a \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch x\u00f3a \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Brazil \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb pha \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0103n m\u1eebng r\u1ea5t cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i cay c\u00fa, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i Barca 4-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-khen-ngoi-malcom-180-192474.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Ernesto Valverde l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i Malcom</span> v\u00ec s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb. Anh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1edbi tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y h\u1ee5t c\u1ee7a Malcom &ndash; HLV Di Francesco c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c khi b\u1ecb Barca c\u01b0\u1edbp h\u00e0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Roma v\u1eabn th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sao tr\u1ebb Brazil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Roma s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Barca 2-4 Roma</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/1/barca-2-4-roma.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day-184-192094.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day-184-192094.html\">Roma nh\u1eafn Barca: &ldquo;Mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf qua v\u1ee5 Malcom, v\u1eady \u0111\u01b0a Messi \u0111\u00e2y&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nCay c\u00fa xen l\u1eabn h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 cho n\u1ed7i nh\u1ee5c b\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1edbp m\u1ea5t Malcom. Theo \u0111\u00f3, AS Roma y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Barca nh\u1ea3 Messi cho h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\">Malcom &ndash; Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft AS Roma. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh?</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4946","checkdouble":"192490"},{"date":"19:37 01/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/8: Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-18-barca-bi-mat-dam-phan-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/8.</h2><h2>Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Pogba\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18 Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18 Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/193541-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 1/8: Barca b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nT\u1edd  Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barcelona \u0111ang t\u0103m tia si\u00eau sao Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a  Man United. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c  k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Eric Abidal c\u1ee7a Barca t\u1ea1i LA c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y. Pogba \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng  \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford nh\u01b0ng Man United v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f3 th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh  tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n khi Pogba c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2021.\r\n<h2>Giroud \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n Cobham. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a The Blues kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111ang t\u00ednh to\u00e1n b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai khi Marseille \u0111ang b\u00e0y t\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh.</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Liverpool gia nh\u1eadp Sheffield United</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i teen Ben Woodburn \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Sheffield United theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 7, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin cho th\u1ea5y Woodburn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Sheffield United v\u00e0 Norwich. Nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i HLV Klopp \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Woodburn l\u00e0 s\u00e2n Bramall Lane.</div>\r\n<h2>Everton nh\u1eafm Rojo thay Yerry Mina</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Barcelona y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Yerry Mina. Ph\u00eda Everton kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed n\u00e0y v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m sang Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Man United. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ph\u00eda Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed y\u00eau c\u1ea7u d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia. V\u00e0 HLV Marco Silva \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<h2>MU nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man United \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 h\u1eadu Mourinho b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Zidane. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Mourinho \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 ba d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Zidane l\u1ea1i \u0111ang r\u1ea3nh r\u1ed7i sau khi r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-18-sao-real-bat-ngo-muon-tro-thanh-doi-thu-cua-ronaldo-184-192440.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 1/8: Sao Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-317-mourinho-duoc-chieu-long-bang-2-bom-tan-184-192358.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 31/7: Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng b\u1eb1ng 2 bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4945","checkdouble":"192496"}]}